                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-212-victim2052 t18210912-212-viclabel1233"></join>. On the 12th of September, about nine o'clock in the morning I was next door to my shop, and was told these tools were stolen off my bench. They had to go through the shop into the back room to get them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210912-212-person2054">
                  HENRY 
                  COVENTRY
               <interp inst="t18210912-212-person2054" type="surname" value="COVENTRY"></interp>
